name: Mobile Strategy Partners
overview:
Mobile Strategy Partners is a strategy consulting firm founded in July 2009 by David Eads to provide an objective source of advice on mobile commerce, mobile banking, mobile payments, and mobile marketing.

Our mission is to help our clients capitalize on the revolutionary advances in mobile technology to increase revenue, lower costs, and win more customers. With global mobile experience at hundreds of name-brand companies across a variety of vertical industries including retail, banking, insurance, investing, and travel, our consultants arguably have most exposure to the latest mobile strategies from around the world. We have insight into mobile efforts on every continent and their rapidly changing competitive forces.
